  <p>To ask the Scottish Executive <a name="QuestionText">how many people received drug and alcohol rehabilitation treatment in each of the past five years.</a></p>

</ques>


<reply id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2001-07-13.S1W-16368.r0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80167" speakername="Iain Gray" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-01/wa0713.htm#se_Minister">

  <p>Information on the total number of individuals receiving drug and alcohol rehabilitation treatment is not available centrally.</p>

