  <p>Notes:</p>

  <p>1. The definition of &quot;new&quot; is (a) the person is attending the particular service for the first time ever or (b) the person has attended before but not within the previous six months.</p>

  <p>2. All figures in this table exclude penal establishment inmates.</p>

  <p>3. Please note alcohol is reported to the database only if it is used as a secondary drug.</p>

  <p>4. In 1999-2000 information was received for the first time from nine agencies in Ayrshire &amp; Arran health board area.</p>

